title: Mahemarket Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, Organic, Raw, Western, Juice bar, Take-out
description: Organic cafeteria located inside a large organic health food store, outside of the city centre. Offers raw food and salads, fresh juices, vegan cooked food, pastries, kale chips, granola, and more. Atmosphere is children friendly and spacious with Wi-Fi access. Reachable by bus number 16 or trolleybusses 1 and 6, stop at Hipodroom.
